yzr demos must feel:

Clean

Minimal

Premium

Fast

Business-friendly

Zero-friction

Visually modern with liquid glass elements

Every demo must work instantly without explanation and reflect the quality of the platform.

1.1 Our Style

White or black background

Subtle gradients

Liquid glass panels (translucent, blurred, rounded)

Soft shadows

Lots of whitespace

Consistent spacing

No clutter

No unnecessary UI

1.2 Our UX Priorities

Make the user feel smart, not confused

Guide them step-by-step, small decisions at a time

Never surprise them with noise or popups

Make the end-to-end flow delightful

Every click should give feedback

Default to "guided" unless user explicitly picks "chat"

